node.text: We’re proud to partner with the Rare Impact Fund to bring you an opportunity to use your points for good. Visit the Rewards Bazaar to redeem your Beauty Insider points for a Charity Reward, and we will donate, on your behalf, to @rarebeauty’s Rare Impact Fund to support organizations that expand access to mental health services in schools and educational settings, with a focus on underserved communities. Don’t forget to mark your calendar for tomorrow at 10am PT to learn more about the Rare Impact Fund on Instagram Live ⏰
